Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:38.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno arrived at the royal \Ncapital of the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.68,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the kingdom dreams \Nof becoming a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:46.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights Entrance Exam\Nwas about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:13.46,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}The Magic Knights Entrance Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:17.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:20.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:25.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.65,0:01:27.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:31.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:37.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:43.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:48.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:53.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.14,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:02.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:22.30,sign_3305_9_The_Clover_Kingd,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1034)}The Clover Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:28.08,sign_3305_9_The_Clover_Kingd,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(980,1)}Castle Town Kikka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.73,main,Grocer,0000,0000,0000,,They're fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.22,main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,One sec. It's almost done roasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:53.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They have so many different \Nkinds of staves and items!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But they're so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:57.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's so different from our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that where the Wizard King is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.55,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,And probably the king, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So that means that'll be my castle someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.92,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You mean mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll let you live there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.86,main,Rebecca,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. Don't cry. Let's hurry \Nback and get ready to open up the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of everyone back at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:36.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sister and the others\Nare lonely now that I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:38.02,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:41.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:51.71,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's so nice and quiet. \NWhat a relief to have Asta gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.69,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.25,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,I-I really mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.95,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,They've probably reached \Nthe royal capital by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:03.38,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the Magic Knights Exam goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.61,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.01,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.90,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.23,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.03,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So where do they hold the \NEntrance Exam, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Probably over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:30.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Grilled purple snake. It was super cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.81,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone want some grilled purple snakes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.83,main,Old lady,0000,0000,0000,,that I just happened to \Ncatch somewhere or other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.41,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:41.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's super nutritious and will \Ngive you lots of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance. Let's go. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.89,main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best on the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.17,main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Clover Kingdom's hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.80,main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,The future of the kingdom is in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:08.68,main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:11.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know him... \NYou don't know him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:22.30,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're #163. All right, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuno from Hage Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.55,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno from Hage...\NCould I see your grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.39,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A f-four-leaf clover...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.98,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,So that's who everyone's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.72,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.38,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really a four-leaf clover?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.81,main,Amy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:44.82,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're #164. All right, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:49.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asta, also from Hage Village!\NHere's my grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.44,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.08,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really a grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Of course it is! Take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.14,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.13,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're #165.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:15.03,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! He must be a real go-getter if he \Ncame here all the way from the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:24.07,main,Synana,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm getting really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.03,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ow! What the heck are these birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:29.18,main,Tanoso,0000,0000,0000,,The infamous anti-birds of the exam venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.36,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Really? These things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:34.45,main,Tanoso,0000,0000,0000,,The weaker your magical powers, \Nthe more these guys flock to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.11,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Little pests...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.21,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.42,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,None of the birds are going to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.74,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's the guy from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.33,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,From earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:51.51,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,He's from some remote village called Hage,\Nyet he's got a four-leaf grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.55,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... A four-leaf? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:05.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One of us is going to become the Wizard King.\NOur legend's beginning now, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.54,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:09.03,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Become the Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:13.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show you just how much \NI've grown in six months...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are these birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.58,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.78,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.29,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty bad, even for \Nsomeone from the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me, you stupid birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:34.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They finally flew off somewhere. \NHey, sorry for bumping into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.22,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's his problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.52,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap. He's got the eyes of a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,His neck's so thick! No mage looks like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:47.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about an intimidating presence! \NIs he really my age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:51.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, wait... You shouldn't \Njudge a book by its cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.78,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Be friendly. Just be friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:58.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you look old!\NYou must've had a hard life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you're ready to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.59,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,His looks weren't a lie at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.59,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is!\NWhat are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to end this little twerp's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.09,main,Synana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:22.13,main,Rooney,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the great Finral Roulacase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.60,main,Rooney,0000,0000,0000,,The user of rare spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:30.57,main,Tanoso,0000,0000,0000,,He's famous for being so girl-crazy\Nthat it gets in the way of his duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:35.49,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,And that's... Gordon Agrippa!\NThe expert on incantation magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:39.87,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he's impossible \Nto talk to... and also scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:45.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, cut it out! A Magic Knights Squad \NCaptain shouldn't kill an exam candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:49.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you even come down here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I went to take a dump and got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:55.47,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Captain? You mean he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.34,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord of Destruction, Yami Sukehiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:09:00.78,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Ten... Nine... Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What're you counting down to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The end of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.85,main,Amy,0000,0000,0000,,Yami?! The Captain of the Black Bulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.03,main,Rooney,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:12.06,main,Rooney,0000,0000,0000,,The cost they incur in damages exceeds \Nthe successes they're credited for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.78,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there isn't a single \Ndecent Magic Knight on that squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:19.73,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,A playboy and a guy who \Ncan't communicate... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.91,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wouldn't want to join that squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.18,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I picked the wrong guy to mess with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.67,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My head's seriously going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.77,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, the exam is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you get to live a little longer, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:54.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Better take good care of \Nthe life you just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:04.33,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I wish the captain would kill me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.83,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:14.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:20.78,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been rough, having Captain Yami\Nof the Black Bulls in your face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:24.05,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Sekke. Sekke Bronzazza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.89,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asta! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:52.04,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nozel Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.26,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Captain of the \NSilver Eagles, Nozel Silva!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.07,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the captains of \Nthe Magic Knights Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:11:00.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's some hairstyle! Isn't it hard \Nto see with that thing in his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:09.25,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1025,1041)}Captain of the Crimson Lion Kings\N{\fs30}Fuegoleon Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:07.25,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Crimson Lion Kings,\NFuegoleon Vermillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.78,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,As the name "Crimson" suggests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.35,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,he's a user of flame creation magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.40,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:18.44,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Green Praying Mantises \N{\fs30}Jack the Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:18.44,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Green Praying Mantises,\NJack the Ripper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's a praying mantis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.16,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You know, a mantis. Like, the bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:26.30,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Captain Jack's severing \Nmagic can split the earth in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:32.42,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to be a mantis.\NBugs are super lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:40.67,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Blue Rose Knights\N{\fs30}Charlotte Roselei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:40.67,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Blue Rose Knights,\NCharlotte Roselei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.66,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Sister Lily's prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:49.85,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Purple Orcas\N{\fs30}Gueldre Poizot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.85,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Purple Orcas,\NGueldre Poizot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:54.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in seamy guys like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:12:00.28,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Coral Peacocks\N{\fs30}Dorothy Unsworth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:58.79,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Coral Peacocks,\NDorothy Unsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.28,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is she walking in her sleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.83,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, all she does is sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:04.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then how'd she become a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:08.99,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,She probably has an amazing power \Nyou'd never expect her to possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:16.17,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Aqua Deer\N{\fs30}Rill Boismortier
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:14.71,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Aqua Deer,\NRill Boismortier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.17,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he pretty young?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.36,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Rill is nineteen, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nineteen?! He's only four \Nyears older than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The path to becoming the Wizard King\Nmight be shorter than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:30.04,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Wizard King, eh? \NThat's a pretty big dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.02,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,But for the next Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.90,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,They say he's the most promising candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:48.23,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the most powerful \NMagic Knights Squad, the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:51.29,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1005,1)}Captain of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}William Vangeance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.45,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,William Vangeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.54,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The members of his squad \Nhave utmost faith in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.06,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,and it's said that in the last battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:01.01,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,it was Captain William who \Ntook the enemy general's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.04,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could get into the Golden Dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.04,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,The Silver Eagles would be great, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:12.77,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. Only royal and noble elites make \Nit into the Golden Dawn and Silver Eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:20.67,sign_15478_150_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,913)}Captain of the Black Bulls\N{\fs30}Yami Sukehiro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:21.65,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Pain in the ass... Can't we \Njust get this over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.60,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important exam that will \Ndecide the futures of these youths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.24,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,We need you to take \Nthis a bit more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, Mr. Serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.03,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,The captains are all gathered in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:36.79,main,Bg,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.57,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that each of the Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:43.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Captains has the strength \Nof a hundred mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.72,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,One of these individuals will \Nbecome the next Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:54.01,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! The Wizard King wouldn't \Nbother coming down to the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:57.60,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle in itself that all the \Ncaptains have gathered in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.73,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:08.78,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.\NI will be conducting this exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:13.95,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Magic tree, descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's still amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:47.94,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the man who's \Nclosest to the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:55.06,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the Magic \NKnights Entrance Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:06.74,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,We will now have you all take several tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.92,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,The nine of us will evaluate \Nyour performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:15.22,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,and then we will select the candidates \Nthat we would like to add to our squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.96,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,If chosen, you will join that squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.10,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,If you're chosen by more than one squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.91,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,you may choose the squad \Nyou would like to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:26.00,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, those who \Nare not chosen by any captain
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:29.99,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,are not qualified to join the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.95,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get into the Magic\NKnights, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.58,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,For the first exam, we will have \Nyou get on those brooms and fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.14,main,Amy,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.41,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:45.19,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Mages who can control their magical powers \Nshould be able to this instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.80,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It is the most basic way for mages to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:52.47,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot fly on a broom, \Nyou shouldn't even be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.89,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,All right, begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:09.42,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Just by observing this, we can get a good \Nidea of what kind of mages they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:12.24,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a few candidates this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:21.21,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,For a kid from the boonies, \Nhe's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.62,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,The genius chosen by the four-leaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:36.85,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much one might be lacking\Nin talent, they should at least float.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.41,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.25,main,Synana,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.64,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we're down one rival already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.23,main,Tanoso,0000,0000,0000,,What is he even doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.74,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, this should be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:58.53,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Loosen up a little bit. Just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.50,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Loosen up, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're a decent guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't float...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.59,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:26.22,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. There's no need for royalty \Nto take the same exam as the peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:30.69,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Your destination has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.36,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Do not take unnecessary action.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:35.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brother Nozel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:39.43,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence itself is unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:53.30,sign_3305_9_The_Clover_Kingd,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Ability Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.55,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.30,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.55,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:59.14,sign_3305_9_The_Clover_Kingd,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Ability Control Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.14,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Just do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:06.27,sign_3305_9_The_Clover_Kingd,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Creation Magic Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.46,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.13,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.27,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Next, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:12.07,sign_3305_9_The_Clover_Kingd,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Developmental Magic Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.92,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.07,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.81,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The next exam \Nshall be the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.45,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You will engage in actual combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.00,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be battling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:32.79,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You will pair off and fight with your partner.\NYou may use your grimoires to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:36.06,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose, it'll severely \Naffect our evaluations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.72,main,Gayaya,0000,0000,0000,,Picking the right opponent will be key.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:44.22,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting is our duty.\NShow us your true abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.73,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as one of you yields or becomes \Nunable to fight, the exam will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:52.57,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,There will be mages who can use \Nhealing magic on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.48,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,So fight to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:59.06,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap! All I've been doing so far is yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:02.59,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stand out by fighting \Nsomeone who looks strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:05.74,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... I need to find \Nsomeone to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.79,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Fight me, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:15.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke! You're willing to \Nfight a loser like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.18,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,But of course! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.39,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,First combatants, come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.47,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:34.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's both give it our all and fight fair, \Nso we can achieve our goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:42.24,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to try so hard anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.37,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,you filthy little rat that \Nwandered into the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:49.10,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for making me \Nlook even better so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:53.26,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get into the Magic Knights and \Ndo my best for the both of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.58,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,and have a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:58.45,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, you miserable peasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.17,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back to your village in the boonies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:05.98,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,and continue enjoying your crappy little life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.22,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:14.05,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke chose the weakest-looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:15.61,main,Amy,0000,0000,0000,,Sekke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.15,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.43,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,No holding back, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.41,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Asta! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:34.42,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bronze Creation Magic: \NSekke Magnum Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.11,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:40.26,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's bronzified and protects me\Nas it shoots out magical bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.17,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It's offense and defense all in one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:48.33,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,It'll block all of your lame attacks, \Nwhich will show off my defensive powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:51.80,italics,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,and then I'll finish you off \Nonce you've worn yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty decent for an exam candidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he look like that spiky bug\Nfrom the Mimo Amazon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.07,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to hold back.\NCome at me! Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:06.32,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Make sure you struggle as much \Nas you can to make things exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.21,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.23,main,Tanoso,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.03,main,Bumoda,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:28.03,main,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joining
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:38.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights so I can have a\Ngood time and avoid working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:43.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to work my butt off \Nand become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:59.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:06.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:14.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:20.98,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:24.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:28.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:35.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:42.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:49.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:56.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:01.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
