Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:23.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta vs. the Anti-Birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:25.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:28.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get away from me! Buzz off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:31.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Hey! What the heck are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:35.14,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:38.06,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuno! Ow, ow, ow! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! I haven't really \Ndone much up to this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:44.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not done yet! I can still do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:47.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pass, no matter what!
